      "id": "overview",
      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the development of a custom e-commerce platform, designed as a clone of posterized.in, utilizing the MERN stack for a full-stack implementation. It includes a customer-facing storefront with dynamic product listings, filtering, search, a shopping cart, and a multi-step checkout, alongside a protected admin dashboard for managing products, users, and orders. The platform will feature secure authentication via Google OAuth, integrated payment processing with Razorpay, and media storage via Cloudinary, all deployed on Vercel."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Product Listing**: Displays all posters available for sale, organized by categories like Art, Movies, and Minimalist.\n- **Filter Products**: Allows users to filter the product catalog based on categories, styles, or other relevant attributes.\n- **Search Products**: Enables visitors to search for specific posters using keywords.\n- **View Product Details**: Shows detailed information for each poster, including images, description, and price.\n- **Add to Cart**: Allows customers to add selected posters to a persistent shopping cart.\n- **Multi-step Checkout**: Guides customers through a secure process to complete their purchase, including shipping and payment details.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Provides a way for visitors to send inquiries to the website administrators.\n- **View Admin Dashboard**: Access to a protected area for managing the e-commerce operations.\n- **Manage Products**: Allows administrators to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on poster listings.\n- **Manage Users**: Enables viewing registered users and their activity on the platform.\n- **Manage Orders**: Provides functionality to view orders, update shipping statuses, and manage transaction details."
    },
    {
      "id": "structure",
      "title": "## Structure",
      "content": "- **Header (Reusable)**: Contains the site logo, navigation links (e.g., Home, Shop, About, Contact), and user account/cart icons.\n- **Footer (Reusable)**: Includes copyright information, links to social media, and essential site links.\n- **Homepage**: Serves as the main landing page, potentially featuring featured products or collections.\n- **Shop Page**: Hosts the dynamic product listing, filtering, and search functionalities.\n- **Product Detail Page**: Displays comprehensive information for a single poster.\n- **Cart Page**: Shows the items added to the shopping cart and allows for quantity adjustments.\n- **Checkout Flow**: A multi-step process for completing an order.\n- **Contact Page**: Contains the contact form for user inquiries.\n- **Admin Dashboard**: A secure section for managing products, users, and orders."
    }
